overview: Gina Valentina and Lilly Ford have taken up a new cause and cut up their bras. Their stepdads aren't happy with the girl's destruction and swap daughters and teach them who's boss! Alex Coal and Kimber Woods are so over taking care of their sick stepdads. To get them to pass out, the girls decide to swap and fuck their dads and then sneak off when they fall asleep! Adrian Hush and Cara May cuddle with their stepdad's during a scary movie but their hands find even more comfort wrapped around the dad's rock-hard cocks! Niki Snow and Zoey Monroe are tired of being broke and come up with the idea of turning each others' stepdad into a sugar stepdaddy - all they have to do is spread their legs!
title: Daughter Swap 9
